<D>__{that's o.k.}
<P>__{(to naeem)}
<D>__{why don't you go grab one of my spare violins?}
<A>__{naeem happily runs to the extra violins at the front of the room; mrs. adisa nods to roberta with a look of gratitude, then exits. roberta crosses back to the front of the room.}
<C>__{roberta}
<P>__{(to class)}
<D>__{let's try it again.}
<A>__{they begin again, and we see naeem take out a violin and join in. as they play, roberta's ears perk up at something she's hearing. she crosses to lucy.}
<C>__{roberta}
<D>__{what are you playing?}
<C>__{lucy}
<D>__{twinkle.}
<C>__{roberta}
<P>__{(to class)}
<D>__{everyone stop!}
